<D>__{you so smart. tell me about your brothers.}
<C>__{denver}
<D>__{well..they're names were howard and..}
<A>__{as denver continues, beloved steps towards her and begins to touch her face examining her lips, her nose, her skin as if it were a rose to admire. denver drinks in the attention, her heart expanding with love with every touch from this strange creature.}
<C>__{denver}
<D>__{..and....and bulgar...at night, we used to..crawl into bed together..i'd lay down on bul's lap and howard would tell us die witch stories. he said they would protect us...and if i learned them, they would protect me if ever they were gone...}
